===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term/t|la|Lacōnicus||Spartan}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|Λακωνικός||Laconian|tr=Lakōnikos|lang=grc}}. [[Laconia]] was the region inhabited and ruled by the Spartans, who were known for their [[brevity]] in speech.

